These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, sports, musical, western, drama, time-travel
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: punk, gospel, d&b, dubstep, ambient, techno, folk
The people prefer 7 different types of sport: weightlifting, badminton, ice-hockey, snowboarding, cricket, handball, basketball
 1. the person watching western movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
 3. the person who's sport is basketball is between the fan of gospel and the fan of punk##2
 4. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 5. the fan of gospel is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is the person who's sport is basketball##1
 7. the fan of dubstep is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person watching western movies##2
 8. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
 9. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is the fan of d&b##1
11. the fan of techno is the person watching musical movies##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
13. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the fan of ambient##1
14. the person watching drama movies is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person who's sport is basketball##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | western | mystery     | drama | spy | musical | time-travel  | sports  |
| Music-Genre   | punk  | dubstep        | gospel  | folk     | techno   | d&b       | ambient   |
| Sport         | badminton   | basketball | snowboarding    | ice-hockey  | cricket | handball | weightlifting |

