The people prefer 7 different types of sport: surfing, rugby, lacrosse, golf, biathlon, skateboarding, ice-hockey
The people use 7 different means of transport: motorbike, van, jet-ski, taxi, subway, airplane, helicopter
 1. the french is on the right of the person driving the van##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 3. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the person who's sport is golf is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the person who's sport is surfing is the spanish##1
 6. the turkish is the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the turkish is between the person who's sport is ice-hockey and the person driving the helicopter##2
 8. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the brazilian##1
 9. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
10. the italian is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
11. the brazilian is on the right of the turkish##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is the french##1
13. the australian is on the left of the turkish##1
14. the australian is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
15. the french is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
