10. the mechanic is on the right of the social-worker##1
11. the person driving the quad-bike is the security-guard##1
12. the mechanic is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
13. the person drinking mirinda is on the left of the electrician##1
14. the person driving the motorbike is the person drinking almond-milk##1
15. the person driving the car is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1

