The people have 7 different jobs:  chef, security-guard, designer, police-officer, doctor, teacher, analyst
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: folk, jazz, pop, rock, country, ambient, gospel
7 different pets are kept: lizard, goat, turtle, goldfish, frog, fish, pony
 1. the owner of the fish is on the left of the designer##1
 2. the owner of the fish is between the fan of country and the fan of pop##2
 3. the fan of folk is the owner of the goat##1
 4. the fan of gospel is on the left of the teacher##1
 5. the fan of folk is the chef##1
 6. the designer is in the middle##1
 7. the doctor is the fan of ambient##1
 8. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the pony##1
 9. the fan of folk is the owner of the goat##1
10. the analyst is the owner of the frog##1
11. the chef is on the right of the police-officer##1
12. the fan of gospel is on the left of the teacher##1
13. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the turtle##1
14. the fan of jazz is on the left of the chef##1
15. the analyst is on the right of the fan of country##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | security-guard | teacher | doctor | designer  | analyst   | police-officer | chef      |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | pop        | ambient    | country     | rock     | jazz   | folk        |
| Pet           | lizard   | turtle       | fish    | goldfish | frog | pony   | goat |

