.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-17::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: skydiving, drawing, chess, card-games, puzzles, collecting, reading
7 different pets are kept: pony, rabbit, fish, ferret, hamster, bird, snake
The people use 7 different means of transport: roller, skateboard, tram, airplane, van, helicopter, jet-ski
 1. the person driving the jet-ski is between the person who's hobby is drawing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##2
 2. the person driving the jet-ski is the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the owner of the hamster is in the middle##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 5. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 6. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 7. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the owner of the ferret##1
 8. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person driving the van##1
10. the person driving the airplane is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
11. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
12. the person who's hobby is reading is the owner of the hamster##1
13. the person driving the airplane is the owner of the bird##1
14. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person driving the roller##1
15. the person driving the tram is on the left of the person who's hobby is collecting##1

.:: Answer ::.
