 2. the owner of the chinchilla is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 3. the person who's sport is handball is on the right of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1
 6. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in the middle##1
 7. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 8. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the owner of the bird##1
 9. the person watching time-travel movies is between the person watching epic movies and the person who's sport is water-polo##2
10. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
11. the person watching musical movies is the owner of the cat##1
12. the person watching time-travel movies is in the middle##1
13. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
14. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
