.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-20::.
There are 7 different favourite beverages: lemonade, water, soy-milk, hot-chocolate, milk, tea, juice
The people have 7 different hobbies: collecting, baking, magic-tricks, sudoku, chess, drawing, woodworking
7 different pets are kept: horse, mouse, turtle, fish, hedgehog, bird, goat
 1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 2. the owner of the bird is in the middle##1
 3. the person drinking water is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the person drinking juice is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 5. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the far right##1
 6. the owner of the bird is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 8. the owner of the fish is between the person who's hobby is magic-tricks and the owner of the turtle##2
 9. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
10. the person who's hobby is sudoku is in the middle##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
13. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
14. the person who's hobby is baking is between the owner of the goat and the person who's hobby is woodworking##2
15. the owner of the goat is the person drinking juice##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
| Beverage   | juice  | tea   | milk   | hot-chocolate        | soy-milk     | water | lemonade       |
| Hobby      | collecting | baking | woodworking | sudoku | magic-tricks  | chess   | drawing |
| Pet        | goat   | mouse     | horse     | bird      | hedgehog | fish    | turtle      |

 